{"tid":2356781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾任義工 周小龍：港人硬淨唔會怕","createTime":"2021-01-07T04:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T06:43:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a748889a4c2087f5d9e84c67773950c4abaa7c6","tid":2356781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/ESTEQPHJ75FDPB2MFJZ2CVMCQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FESTEQPHJ75FDPB2MFJZ2CVMCQQ%2F&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5kYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=ffe9fca9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FESTEQPHJ75FDPB2MFJZ2CVMCQQ%2F&h=6de062e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/ESTEQPHJ75FDPB2MFJZ2CVMCQQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n曾任義工 周小龍：港人硬淨唔會怕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z4F8oAOka12BD_u-rtaIusH6VFM=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OKNNU24PEZFZ7H6C74RWTAAI4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz4F8oAOka12BD_u-rtaIusH6VFM%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOKNNU24PEZFZ7H6C74RWTAAI4Q.jpg&h=6bbe30e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曾任票站義工的周小龍稱無懼被捕。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方秋後算賬大搜捕，惟一眾於參選人背後默默支持的義工未有畏懼，誓言齊上齊落。在票站擔任義工的連鎖童裝店Chickeeduck行政總裁周小龍明言，不擔心因參與初選被捕，「我光明正大行得正企得正、理直氣壯，唔覺得有咩俾佢抽秤到我」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：政治素人登廣告拍片 被指策劃者<br />\n<br />\n周形容今次事件反映政權「沒有最荒謬，只有更荒謬」，批評藉大搜捕製造寒蟬效應，「但香港人係好tough（硬淨），點會怕你呢啲！」<br />\n<br />\n周小龍又強調，民主派初選早有先例，亦完全合法，立法會議員亦有否決議案的權利，「立法會否決議案係正常，唔通做橡皮圖章。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：印裔「曼聯英雄」被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李傲然：退縮愧對支持者<br />\n<br />\n另一有份擔任初選義工的油尖旺區議員李傲然指，無法估計國安法下被捕風險，「老實講係冇得擔心，從來冇人知佢嘅界線喺邊度，既來之則安之」，但強調不會因此退縮，「如果因為擔心，就將條紅線越退越後，對唔對得住曾支持過我哋嘅香港人呢？」<br />\n<br />\n李傲然又批評保安局局長李家超形容初選為「歹毒的計劃」，是以小人之心度君子之腹。。。。。。。。，將香港人視為敵人，最終將自食惡果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5mvT0D2eqL2MD0T9At2NEznL9Vo=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WEVEX7KHVFEKDGXMJYIUJBGRFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5mvT0D2eqL2MD0T9At2NEznL9Vo%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWEVEX7KHVFEKDGXMJYIUJBGRFI.jpg&h=d16172e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李傲然斥政府拒聽民意，與港人為敵。"},{"pid":"7e79e16dfbb31c3711f24b4042c4f418eacdbf0e","tid":2356781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}